<td style="text-align:right;"> cmd + delete </td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:left;"> <strong>Search</strong>  </td>
<td style="text-align:right;">  cmd + shift + h </td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:left;"> <strong>Refresh</strong>  </td>
